{"tid":1795711,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈 - 外國戰線","createTime":"2019-12-24T06:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T14:34:27.000Z","uid":267914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a27f171a4109c62c6ad709629042deffc308887b","tid":1795711,"uid":267914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/主权财富基金\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%83%E8%B4%A2%E5%AF%8C%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlppMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=e643ed2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/主权财富基金</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇可能成立到一個黃色既主權基金，<br />\n足已影響到世界？"},{"pid":"485ae246b8b6d9aaf994c516e3071d5c0f57056a","tid":1795711,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去大半年，大家既生活都過得好壓抑，好似見到有希望但係又唔知前路候點。有人或者係依大半年同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手離婚，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸又或者有家歸不得，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlppMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=8163dacd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243338d121885e940d0d25448a75936a8ebfe8cc","tid":1795711,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a27f171a4109c62c6ad709629042deffc308887b","tid":1795711,"uid":267914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/主权财富基金\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%83%E8%B4%A2%E5%AF%8C%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlppMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=e643ed2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/主权财富基金</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇可能成立到一個黃色既主權基金，<br />\n足已影響到世界？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都照推，順手借個位<br />\n（重要原則）想經濟攬炒，必須先紅後藍，否則只會事倍功半<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}